      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "The DISPLAY CHARACTERISTICS panel is modifiable table that may be"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "changed to alter the way a specific SPF/PC function is displayed."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "For example, by modifying the \"Panel Split Separator,\" the display"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "attributes of the dotted Split Line is changed the next time it is"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "displayed."
